<paragraph blockId="3.[151,701,153,215]" box="[151,401,189,215]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">
(
<figureCitation box="[159,310,189,215]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–24" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1767,1792]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,189,1727]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,179,1739]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 1–24. Habitus (dorsal view and lateral view), crown, pronotum and scutellum (dorsal view), and face. 1–4, Takagioma pagoda sp. nov.; 5–8, Takagioma rostra sp. nov.; 9–12, Takagioma gladius sp. nov.; 13–16, Takagioma curvata sp. nov.; 17–20, Takagioma anguis sp. nov.; 21–24, Takagioma longicauda sp. nov" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677809" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3677809/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Figures 9–12</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[322,393,189,215]" captionStart="FIGURES 40–49" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1934,1959]" captionTargetBox="[210,1369,192,1897]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[206,1382,181,1908]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 40–49. Takagioma gladius sp. nov. 40, crown, pronotum and scutellum, dorsal view; 41, forewing; 42, hind wing; 43, abdominal apodemes; 44, genital capsule, ventral view; 45, pygofer hook, dorsal view; 46, subgenital plate, ventral view; 47, aedeagus and connective, ventral view; 48, aedeagus and connective, lateral view; 49, paramere, ventral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677815" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3677815/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">40–49</figureCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,261,863]" box="[151,759,261,288]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,315,262,288]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Measurement</emphasis>
. Male, 2.95–3.15mm (including wing).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,261,863]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,297,324]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Description.</emphasis>
Body ochraceous with whitish stripe thin on vertex; eyes brown; pronotum with a brown triangle patch centrally. Face brown with apical margin ocherous. Forewing yellowish in basal 4/5, hind wing with CuA branched.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,261,863]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">
Abdominal apodeme reaching end of 3rd abdominal sternite (
<figureCitation box="[887,972,405,431]" captionStart="FIGURES 40–49" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1934,1959]" captionTargetBox="[210,1369,192,1897]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[206,1382,181,1908]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 40–49. Takagioma gladius sp. nov. 40, crown, pronotum and scutellum, dorsal view; 41, forewing; 42, hind wing; 43, abdominal apodemes; 44, genital capsule, ventral view; 45, pygofer hook, dorsal view; 46, subgenital plate, ventral view; 47, aedeagus and connective, ventral view; 48, aedeagus and connective, lateral view; 49, paramere, ventral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677815" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3677815/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Fig. 43</figureCitation>
). Male pygofer hook long and curved laterad posteriorly (
<figureCitation box="[341,471,441,468]" captionStart="FIGURES 40–49" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1934,1959]" captionTargetBox="[210,1369,192,1897]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[206,1382,181,1908]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 40–49. Takagioma gladius sp. nov. 40, crown, pronotum and scutellum, dorsal view; 41, forewing; 42, hind wing; 43, abdominal apodemes; 44, genital capsule, ventral view; 45, pygofer hook, dorsal view; 46, subgenital plate, ventral view; 47, aedeagus and connective, ventral view; 48, aedeagus and connective, lateral view; 49, paramere, ventral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677815" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3677815/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Figs 44, 45</figureCitation>
). Subgenital plate triangular with 3 macrosetae (
<figureCitation box="[1009,1093,441,468]" captionStart="FIGURES 40–49" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1934,1959]" captionTargetBox="[210,1369,192,1897]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[206,1382,181,1908]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 40–49. Takagioma gladius sp. nov. 40, crown, pronotum and scutellum, dorsal view; 41, forewing; 42, hind wing; 43, abdominal apodemes; 44, genital capsule, ventral view; 45, pygofer hook, dorsal view; 46, subgenital plate, ventral view; 47, aedeagus and connective, ventral view; 48, aedeagus and connective, lateral view; 49, paramere, ventral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677815" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3677815/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Fig. 46</figureCitation>
). Paramere long with cephalad and caudal part slim, central part with short lobe (
<figureCitation box="[710,794,477,503]" captionStart="FIGURES 40–49" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1934,1959]" captionTargetBox="[210,1369,192,1897]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[206,1382,181,1908]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 40–49. Takagioma gladius sp. nov. 40, crown, pronotum and scutellum, dorsal view; 41, forewing; 42, hind wing; 43, abdominal apodemes; 44, genital capsule, ventral view; 45, pygofer hook, dorsal view; 46, subgenital plate, ventral view; 47, aedeagus and connective, ventral view; 48, aedeagus and connective, lateral view; 49, paramere, ventral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677815" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3677815/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Fig. 49</figureCitation>
). Connective sclerotized with central lobe absent and lateral feet short. Aedeagus sclerotized with dorsoatrium slightly arched in lateral view; aedeagal shaft long, straight, tapering apically and sword-like in ventral view, slightly arched in lateral view (
<figureCitation box="[1048,1178,549,575]" captionStart="FIGURES 40–49" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1934,1959]" captionTargetBox="[210,1369,192,1897]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[206,1382,181,1908]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 40–49. Takagioma gladius sp. nov. 40, crown, pronotum and scutellum, dorsal view; 41, forewing; 42, hind wing; 43, abdominal apodemes; 44, genital capsule, ventral view; 45, pygofer hook, dorsal view; 46, subgenital plate, ventral view; 47, aedeagus and connective, ventral view; 48, aedeagus and connective, lateral view; 49, paramere, ventral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677815" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3677815/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Figs 47, 48</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
