<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,261,863]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,273,694,720]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Notes.</emphasis>
The new species is similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Dworakowska, 1993" authorityName="Dworakowska" authorityYear="1993" box="[617,1083,693,719]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Takagioma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="silvicola">
<emphasis box="[617,843,693,719]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Takagioma silvicola</emphasis>
Dworakowska, 
<quantity box="[1027,1083,693,719]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.06222" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" unit="in" value="1993.0">1993</quantity>
</taxonomicName>
in body coloration, but has the white stripe broader on the vertex and differs from all others of the genus by the slim aedeagal shaft and absence the central lobe of the connective.
</paragraph>
